Hi @sowinski!

The dropbox theme needs a [`headerTemplate` setting](http://mottie.github.io/tablesorter/docs/#headertemplate) that includes an `{icon}` ([demo](http://jsfiddle.net/Mottie/856bzzeL/1000/)):

```js
$(function () {
  $('table').tablesorter({
    theme: 'dropbox',
    // dropbox theme doesn't like a space between the content & icon
    headerTemplate: '{content}{icon}',
    sortList: [[0,0]],
    widgets: ['zebra', 'columns']
  });
});
```

